room_title: Escape room "Prohibition" by Beat the Room in Sacramento
room_description: It is 1928, the peak of the Prohibition era. Your bootlegger gang is trying to secure a reliable booze supplier. However, the much more powerful and influential gang of Al “Scarface” Capone has managed to get a hold of all the local suppliers and they will not disclose their contacts. You have inside information that Capone and his gang have left for 60 minutes. You must gain access to his infamous Speakeasy Bar and steal the list of suppliers before they return or you’ll “swim with the fishes”.
